&lt;li&gt;Reconcile customer payment activity recorded in ticketing systems to third-party processor reporting and merchant account activity to ensure completeness and accuracy.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support reconciliation reporting by compiling transaction-level data and summaries for internal stakeholders (e.g., Manager, Finance, Accounting).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track chargeback activity and support KPI reporting, including status updates and trend monitoring.&lt;/li&gt;
