&lt;li&gt;Provide backup coverage and support across the reconciliation/chargeback function as needed to maintain operational continuity.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist chargeback agents during peak volume periods to support timely processing and completion of required dispute documentation, as needed.&lt;/li&gt;
